					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Alternative way:<br />- Poll for VBL<br />- Wait in timed loop for ~30k cycles<br />- Check VBL flag in $2002, if set =&gt; NTSC<br />- Wait in timed loop for ~4k cycles<br />- Check VBL flag in $2002, if set =&gt; PAL<br />- Otherwise =&gt; Dendy</div>

					
